TextEng: Greetings, Sir. My name is <FullName>.
Who are you?
Hello, sir. Me is <FullName>.
What your name?
I'll be going.
Me go now.
You look familiar, somehow...
Mmmm... me recognizes you, maybe...
Text: 음... 나 너 아는 것 같아...

TextEng: I wonder if I could ask you some questions?
I have some questions for you.
Me want ask something.
<StartCheck>[Lore]</Start> Elaith Craulnober. I've heard that name before.
Text: <StartCheck>[전승지식]</Start> 엘레이스 크롤노버. 전에 그 이름을 들어본 적이 있어요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lore]</Start> Elaith Craulnober. Me hears that name befores.
Text: <StartCheck>[전승지식]</Start> 엘레이스 크롤노버. 나 그 이름 전에 들었어.

TextEng: I'm looking for information on the people that started the plague.
Text: 역병을 일으킨 사람들에 대한 정보를 찾고 있어요.

TextEng: Me look for people who starts plague.
Evermeet is closed to you? Why is that?
Text: 에버밋이 당신에게 닫혔다고요? 왜 그런 거죠?

TextEng: Why Evermeet be closed? You kicked out?
Do you know of anything odd in the area?
Text: 이 지역에서 이상한 일이 있었는지 아세요?

TextEng: You know 'bout weird stuff 'round here?
Please continue.
I hope this story has a point to it.
Me still listening.
Me get bored.
What is this 'Evermeet' you mention?
You say something 'bout "Evermeet." What that?
So what do you intend to do?
So what you do?
I don't really trust you, Elaith.
Text: 엘레이스, 당신을 정말 신뢰할 수가 없네요.

TextEng: Me no trust you.
What kind of reward are we talking here?
What reward if me do it?
Very well, Elaith. I shall help you recover the gems.
Text: 좋습니다, 엘레이스. 보석을 되찾는 걸 도와드리겠습니다.

TextEng: Okay... me get gems for you.
I am not interested in this.
Me no care about stupid gems.
Perhaps I could help?
Maybe me helps?
I might help... for the right price.
Text: 도와줄 수도 있죠... 적절한 대가만 있다면.

TextEng: I coulds help... if price good.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I could get the job done, I assure you.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me could gets it done, me knows.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 해낼 수 있어. 나 알아.

TextEng: Fine. Do it yourself, then.
Okays. You do it, then.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I'd expect some kind of payment up front if you want me to do this.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Okays, but me want coins now, not laters!
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 좋아. 근데 나 돈 지금 줘. 나중에 말고!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Nice story. Unless you want me blabbing it all over town, however, I want some coin up front.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 좋은 이야기네요. 하지만 제가 이걸 온 마을에 떠벌리는 걸 원치 않으시면 선불이 필요해요.

TextEng: Might you have any equipment I could purchase?
Text: 제가 구매할 수 있는 장비가 있으신가요?

TextEng: Maybe you haves stuff I buy?
Retired? A real loss to the profession, I'm sure.
Right. You don't look like you're retired.
Text: 그렇군요. 은퇴한 것 같아 보이지 않는데요.

TextEng: You retire for true, or you just pretendy retire?
Text: 너 진짜 은퇴했어? 아니면 그냥 척하는 거야?

TextEng: Oh, nevermind then.
Okays, no mind then.
I'll take a look.
Me takes peek.
No, that's okay.
Could I buy some equipment from you?
Me buys stuff from you?
I have been thinking about your offer...
Me be thinking 'bout offer...
Tell me who currently has these gems again.
Text: 누가 현재 이 보석들을 가지고 있는지 다시 말해주세요.

TextEng: Say where me finds gems again.
I do have one of the gems right here.
Text: 보석 중 하나를 여기 가지고 있어요.

TextEng: Me has gem right here.
I have the last gem.
Me has last gem.
No, I'll be going.
No, me go now.
Here, Elaith. Take the gem.
Here, you takes it.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> These gems were difficult to acquire. I think I deserve more than you're paying me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이 보석들을 얻는 게 어려웠어요. 당신이 주는 것보다 더 받을 자격이 있다고 생각해요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Gems was hard to gets. Me deserves more than you pays.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 보석 얻기 힘들었어. 나 너 주는 거보다 더 받을 자격 있어.

TextEng: I have the feeling you're shafting me. Pay more or no deal!
Text: 당신이 날 속이는 것 같은데요. 더 주지 않으면 거래 없어요!

TextEng: You cheats me, me knows it! You no gets gem!
Text: 너 나 속여. 나 알아! 너 보석 못 가져!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Threaten]</Start> It'd be a shame if anything happened to your daughter, Elaith.
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> 당신 딸에게 무슨 일이 생긴다면 안타까운 일이겠군요, 엘레이스.

TextEng: Fine. Take the gem.
I'm not frightened of you. You get nothing!
Text: 당신이 무섭지 않아요. 아무것도 못 받을 거예요!

TextEng: Fine. You takes gem.
Me not scared! You gets nothing!
Text: 나 안 무서워! 너 아무것도 못 가져!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lore]</Start> Elaith Craulnober. I've heard that name before.
Text: <StartCheck>[전승지식]</Start> 엘레이스 크롤노버. 전에 그 이름을 들어본 적이 있어요.

TextEng: Might you have any equipment I could purchase?
Text: 제가 구매할 수 있는 장비가 있으신가요?

TextEng: Maybe you haves stuff I buy?
Retired? A real loss to the profession, I'm sure.
Right. You don't look like you're retired.
Text: 그렇군요. 은퇴한 것 같아 보이지 않는데요.

TextEng: You retire for true, or you just pretendy retire?
Text: 너 진짜 은퇴했어? 아니면 그냥 척하는 거야?

TextEng: Oh, nevermind then.
Okays, no mind then.
I'll take a look.
Me takes peek.
No, that's okay.
What you doings here, then?
What are you doing here, then?
Tells me 'bout yourself.
Tell me more about yourself.
<StartCheck>[Lore]</Start> Elaith Craulnober. Me hears that name befores.
Text: <StartCheck>[전승지식]</Start> 엘레이스 크롤노버. 나 그 이름 전에 들었어.
